data.description: Price Drop, and Seller will contribute up to 5,000 towards Buyers Closing Cost. Don't miss out on this pristine, spacious, like new 5BDR 4BATH home.  Enjoy entertaining in both your dining room and eat in kitchen. Living room features a brick fireplace and open floor plan. In the Owner's Suite you will enjoy the soaking tub and tiled shower. Upstairs is a large bonus room,4 bedrooms,2 full baths, and plenty of closet space. Wait till you see the multi use office/studio.There's even more! Tankless Water Heater,Security System, and Extended Patio in backyard. Perfect location! Just minutes from Sparkman Park,Hartselle Aquatic Center, and downtown festivities! What are you waiting for!
